response.original_title: NJPW Road To Power Struggle 2017: Day 12
response.overview: On November 02, 2017, Twin Messe Shizuoka in Shizuoka hosted Day 12 of NJPW Road To Power Struggle 2017, broadcast on an unknown station.  The main event featured Los Ingobernables de Japon (EVIL & SANADA & Tetsuya Naito) vs CHAOS (Kazuchika Okada & Rocky Romero).  The card also featured Hiroshi Tanahashi & Katsuya Kitamura & Togi Makabe vs Juice Robinson & Kota Ibushi.  Other wrestlers on the show include ACH, Ryusuke Taguchi, and Tiger Mask, and more!
response.title: NJPW Road To Power Struggle 2017: Day 12
